"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"BTC分析：\\n\\n一：日MA20线\\n\\n1、买入操作\\n\\n![真突破和假突破](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kRe__Ra__FZ2EvFt5nlzD.png?height=563&width=1803)\\n\\n（1）与日MA20线交叉，判断是否突破\\n\\n        假突破：未来两三天，日MA20还是下降趋势，价格是横盘或者下跌，先观察两天，可以尝试开空（线以下）。\\n\\n       真突破：未来两三天，日MA20上升趋势，并拉开距离，价格连涨几天。\\n\\n![真突破的线集合](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/DNb5PCrOUaQe1caFWpEbp.png?height=813&width=1729)\\n\\n（2）周MA20线  4W是强支撑位\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/N6yo9YE5QIyF_ZWkS2L7x.png?height=609&width=1473)\\n\\n（3）突破启动后，回踩也是上车机会\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/RC_IXKwsR-76fukeb6H1t.png?height=651&width=1920)\\n\\n（4）币有利好，大户市价买入\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Ep7iTt4Ztks0PzDyE1kzh.png?height=638&width=1920)\\n\\n（5）跌到超级底部，触底反弹\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/cXWr4pqxZu_NNajPr-qHX.png?height=656&width=1920)\\n\\n二、实操日MA20\\n\\n1、2020-12-12到2021-1-20  共38天  18600-→35700 涨幅：91%\\n\\n![日MA20 开多](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/pMKsBbrqfOAC7MOAUDxMk.png?height=614&width=1911)\\n\\n2、2021-7-23到2021-9-7 共44天  32600→48700 涨幅：49%\\n\\n![日MA20 开多](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/GLbT5_Cncb4o9SujEwmlr.png?height=604&width=1887)\\n\\n3、2021-10-1到2021-11-16 共47天 44700→63000 涨幅：40%\\n\\n![日MA20 开多](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/EdN_jymNTiqHfVRYz9zKi.png?height=650&width=1915)\\n\\n**\\\\*开空 63000->42000 跌幅33%**\\n\\n![开空 63000->42000 跌幅33%](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Bi-9IBK2n4btg3_x75L0M.png?height=602&width=1900)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/J5Dm-hvq6nnJ7hfR14FwE.png?height=556&width=1567)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/tXWSCLuYRBjuETsH3N3kd.png?height=616&width=1911)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/y5hn0uRo1kF0pzRY7MdJC.png?height=658&width=1918)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641546018,\"title\":\"MA20线（之上为上升趋势，之下为下降趋势）\"},\"digest\":\"EI52SNnZkfFmvh4Ublals9l2YRlaDoJrytOJ1LUHvd4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2844a343BD6bfd554F7f42FD2b2Fd6Ff1636E262\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"alg\\\":\\\"ES256\\\",\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"8G0pBH6FnQbWmUUDWAfsJENQxFjJBITdxG3pycE2Qbk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_jofEGZuFb0z2tPVhdlhdXINcBQ3UEfD1i4eRGRsBjg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"E4kWPO98OmA5CbERmPU8w-hCri3hWd27L8A7s5GUTdyZJK7-O2xkMG4Hj3BQiI5De1OpBkaIEPKzTB24tFFqjw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xde6633940f3ebdd38939aba04fa57c4081ef5ffd0d92d75e6c617c3ea7fb5e226dad2114f7e85ffbe67846022a7d9349e4f867a99dfac62c08e4e522e5f7441a1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"alg\\\":\\\"ES256\\\",\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"8G0pBH6FnQbWmUUDWAfsJENQxFjJBITdxG3pycE2Qbk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_jofEGZuFb0z2tPVhdlhdXINcBQ3UEfD1i4eRGRsBjg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"EI52SNnZkfFmvh4Ublals9l2YRlaDoJrytOJ1LUHvd4\"}"